{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/create-flexible-layouts-using-auto-fit","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"css-grid","demoType":null,"title":"Kreirajte dinamičke postavke korišćenjem auto-fit","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><code>auto-fit</code> radi skoro isto kao <code>auto-fill</code>. Jedina razlika je u tome što kada veličina kontejnera premaši ukupnu veličinu svih predmeta, <code>auto-fill</code> nastavlja da ubacuje prazne redove ili kolone i gura vaše predmete sa strane, dok <code>auto-fit</code> skraćuje te prazne redove ili kolone i poravnava vaše predmete kako bi odgovarali veličini kontejnera.</p>\n<p><strong>Napomena:</strong> Ako vaš kontejner ne može da smesti sve stavke na jedan red, on će ih postaviti ispod, u novi red.</p>\n</section>","id":"5a94fe6269fb03452672e462","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>U drugoj mreži, koristite <code>auto-fit</code> zajedno sa <code>repeat</code> da popunite mrežu kolonama širine od najmanje <code>60px</code> i maksimalno <code>1fr</code>. Zatim promenite veličinu prikaza da vidite razliku.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/p/pByETK/c3dPph8","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301127,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/create-flexible-layouts-using-auto-fit"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\r\n  .item1 {\r\n    background: LightSkyBlue;\r\n  }\r\n  .item2 {\r\n    background: LightSalmon;\r\n  }\r\n  .item3 {\r\n    background: PaleTurquoise;\r\n  }\r\n  .item4 {\r\n    background: LightPink;\r\n  }\r\n  .item5 {\r\n    background: PaleGreen;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .container {\r\n    font-size: 40px;\r\n    min-height: 100px;\r\n    width: 100%;\r\n    background: LightGray;\r\n    display: grid;\r\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(60px, 1fr));\r\n    grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\r\n    grid-gap: 10px;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .container2 {\r\n    font-size: 40px;\r\n    min-height: 100px;\r\n    width: 100%;\r\n    background: Silver;\r\n    display: grid;\r\n    /* Only change code below this line */\r\n\r\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(60px, 1fr));\r\n\r\n    /* Only change code above this line */\r\n    grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\r\n    grid-gap: 10px;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n  <div class=\"item1\">1</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item2\">2</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item3\">3</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item4\">4</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item5\">5</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"container2\">\r\n  <div class=\"item1\">1</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item2\">2</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item3\">3</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item4\">4</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item5\">5</div>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Klasa <code>container2</code> treba da ima svojstvo <code>grid-template-columns</code> sa <code>repeat</code> i <code>auto-fit</code> koje popunjava mreže i kolone širine od najmanje <code>60px</code> i maksimalno do <code>1fr</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(\r\n  code,\r\n  /.container2\\s*?{[\\s\\S]*grid-template-columns\\s*?:\\s*?repeat\\s*?\\(\\s*?auto-fit\\s*?,\\s*?minmax\\s*?\\(\\s*?60px\\s*?,\\s*?1fr\\s*?\\)\\s*?\\)\\s*?;[\\s\\S]*}/gi\r\n);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#css-grid","dashedName":"create-flexible-layouts-using-auto-fit","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"css-grid","isFirstStep":false,"template":nul